name: HAMILTON CHAMPIONS TM Canadian Dividend Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of Fund is to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a Canadian equity dividend index. Specifically, the ETF currently seeks to replicate the Solactive Canada Dividend Elite Champions Index The investment objective of fund is to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a Canadian equity dividend index.
